    "deny-r32-tags": "Tier 2 DENY emitted; reason mentions tag taxonomy prefix mismatch.",
    "warn-r47": "Tier 1 advisory emitted (post-write-verify or reminder); does NOT block. Detected by inspecting hook stdout for advisory-class JSON or tier1 message.",
